    "description": "in Exodus, you'll embody the hand of God, leading the Hebrews out of Egypt. With the power to manipulate the environment, you will be able to help your people overcome enemies and obstacles in their path. The game offers a diverse range of challenging puzzles, each world has with a unique twist on the game's mechanics.<br><br>You can tear up the sea for Moses to pass, and restore it ro stop the enemy<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394850/extras/d4fbff4ee581d47706bccd2887fe1d90.poster.avif?t=1692209127\" width=400 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394850/extras/d4fbff4ee581d47706bccd2887fe1d90.webm?t=1692209127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394850/extras/d4fbff4ee581d47706bccd2887fe1d90.mp4?t=1692209127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Other puzzles, require using a combination of multiple interactions with the environment. For example,  in one stage, player need to coordinate a moment of a snake wave with the tearing of the sea so that Moses can pass safely<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394850/extras/95072992bcf4294b33de19a177b1ccaa.poster.avif?t=1692209127\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394850/extras/95072992bcf4294b33de19a177b1ccaa.webm?t=1692209127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394850/extras/95072992bcf4294b33de19a177b1ccaa.mp4?t=1692209127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Or in another stage, use a combination of blended color waves and triggered mirrors in order to open a color-coded gate<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394850/extras/2044661716006eac2a8b37b21e77b0eb.poster.avif?t=1692209127\" width=400 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394850/extras/2044661716006eac2a8b37b21e77b0eb.webm?t=1692209127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394850/extras/2044661716006eac2a8b37b21e77b0eb.mp4?t=1692209127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As the game progresses you are introduced to many varied mechanics and increasingly difficult puzzles built around them",
